# Problem 7: Reverse a String

## Example

```python
Python
```

Output:

```python
nohtyP
```

---

## Recursive Solution

```python
def reverse_string(text):

    if len(text) == 0:
        return ""

    return reverse_string(text[1:]) + text[0]

print(reverse_string("Python"))
```

---

## Built-in Solution

```python
text = "Python"

print(text[::-1])
```

