# Intermediate Recursion Problems

## 8. Find Fibonacci Number

```python
def fibonacci(n):

    if n <= 1:
        return n

    return fibonacci(n - 1) + fibonacci(n - 2)

print(fibonacci(6))
```

Output:

```text
8
```

