# Advanced Recursion Problems

## 11. Check Palindrome

```python
def palindrome(text):

    if len(text) <= 1:
        return True

    if text[0] != text[-1]:
        return False

    return palindrome(text[1:-1])

print(palindrome("madam"))
```

